{"tid":1394923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(尋人）多謝7月28號嗰晚喺元朗西鐵站嗰位絲打","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T14:53:26.000Z","uid":35905,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63fdc666d043a84f3bb86d8dc6af4da85205d86e","tid":1394923,"uid":35905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:48:14.000Z","msg":"代朋友開Po<br />\n朋友喺7月28號嗰晚發夢喺元朗西鐵站到<br />\n同一位絲打一齊俾狗追<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後我位朋友仲同呢位絲打扮情侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁先可以避過俾狗追<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝呢位同我朋友一齊發夢既絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果同我朋友一齊發夢嗰位絲打你有睇到呢個Po<br />\n我朋友話好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為冇你既幫助 <br />\n我嗰位朋友可能已經俾人捉左返狗屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41ff59fd6e659c5e640253d79da1f5fd3b1e807","tid":1394923,"uid":174551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁岩一齊夢遊姐"}]}